                <h1>Essential Guide to Background Phone Checks</h1>
                <p>A background phone check is a process used to verify an individual's identity, history, and credentials. It typically includes criminal records, credit history, and employment verification. This check is essential for employers, landlords, and anyone conducting due diligence to ensure safety and trustworthiness before making important decisions.</p>
